---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Capabilities — Jakar Industries" description="Advanced technologies engineered for mission-critical performance.">
  <article class="article-page">
    <div class="article-hero">
      <video class="article-hero-video" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
        <source src="/videos/hero-jet.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <div class="article-hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="article-hero-content">
        <h1 class="article-title">Our Capabilities</h1>
        <p class="article-subtitle">Advanced technologies for mission success</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">›</span>
        <span class="breadcrumb-current">Capabilities</span>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="article-content">
      <div class="article-body">
        <section class="article-section">
          <p class="intro-text">Built on decades of defense innovation, our capabilities span sensor integration, secure communications, autonomous systems, and advanced data analytics.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="article-section">
          <h2>Sensor Integration</h2>
          <p>Multi-spectrum sensor fusion systems that deliver unified situational awareness across military and public safety operations. Real-time data processing with latency under 100ms.</p>
          <p><strong>Key Technologies:</strong> LIDAR and Radar Fusion, Multi-spectrum Imaging, Real-time Data Processing, Distributed Architecture</p>
        </section>

        <section class="article-section">
          <h2>Secure Communications</h2>
          <p>Military-grade encrypted communication systems with end-to-end security. NATO and NIST compliance standards, interoperable with legacy systems.</p>
          <p><strong>Key Technologies:</strong> Military-Grade Encryption, Quantum-Ready Architecture, Legacy System Interop, Resilient Networks</p>
        </section>

        <section class="article-section">
          <h2>Autonomous Systems</h2>
          <p>Next-generation autonomous platforms with advanced AI decision-making. Unmanned systems for reconnaissance, logistics, and combat support.</p>
          <p><strong>Key Technologies:</strong> AI/ML Integration, Autonomous Navigation, Swarm Coordination, Fail-Safe Operation</p>
        </section>

        <section class="article-section">
          <h2>Data Analytics</h2>
          <p>Advanced analytics platforms that transform raw operational data into actionable intelligence. Predictive modeling and pattern recognition at scale.</p>
          <p><strong>Key Technologies:</strong> Big Data Processing, Predictive Analytics, Pattern Recognition, Real-time Dashboards</p>
        </section>

        <section class="article-section article-highlight">
          <h3>Strategic Platforms</h3>
          
          <div class="platform-item">
            <h4>SENTINEL Defense Platform</h4>
            <p>Integrated command and control system for military operations. Real-time tactical awareness, threat assessment, and response coordination across distributed forces.</p>
            <p><strong>Specs:</strong> 500+ User Nodes | Sub-100ms Latency | 99.99% Uptime | NATO Certified</p>
          </div>

          <div class="platform-item">
            <h4>FIRST RESPONDER Coordination System</h4>
            <p>Purpose-built platform for emergency services and public safety agencies. Unified dispatch, resource management, and inter-agency coordination.</p>
            <p><strong>Specs:</strong> 500+ Agency Support | Mobile Optimized | Disaster Resilient | FIPS 140-2</p>
          </div>

          <div class="platform-item">
            <h4>NEXUS Analytics Engine</h4>
            <p>Enterprise-scale data analytics and intelligence platform. Processes petabytes of operational data to deliver predictive insights and strategic advantage.</p>
            <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Petabyte Scale | AI-Powered Insights | Scalable Architecture | Real-time Processing</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="article-section">
          <h2>Certifications & Compliance</h2>
          <p>We maintain the highest standards of security and compliance: NATO Certified, NIST 800-53, FIPS 140-2, ISO 27001, ITAR Compliant, and Common Criteria.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article-page {
    background-color: #000;
    color: var(--color-white);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .article-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 60vh;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .article-hero-video {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .article-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 0%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 100%
    );
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .article-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .article-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-max);
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .article-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--fs-500);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    background-color: #000;
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .breadcrumb nav {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .breadcrumb-separator {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0.35rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb-current {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }

  .article-content {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .article-body {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #222;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .article-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .article-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-800);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #000;
  }

  .article-section h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0087ca;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .article-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-500);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .article-highlight {
    background: rgba(0, 135, 202, 0.08);
    border-left: 4px solid #0087ca;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .platform-item {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .platform-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .platform-item h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-700);
    color: #0087ca;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .platform-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .article-hero {
      height: 50vh;
    }

    .article-content {
      padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    }

    .article-body {
      padding: 0 var(--space-md);
    }

    .article-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }
  }
</style>
